		<p class="b_comment mb2 long_comment">With our busy lives and our love for having a furry little family member, comes a big responsibility, a lot of worrying and some major expenses. And we never had the luxury to rely on strangers or get help when we needed it the most for our pets.<br><br>Well with Ur Pets Life full list of services and excellent service and care for pets, we can give your our solemn promise that we will always be here for <span class="hide">all our members, that we are always willing to help in anything you require and most importantly that we will make sure we minimize your spends on all your shopping needs to reach to a point where these savings will work as your pet insurance.<br><br>Now of course every business owners will tell you the same beautiful words and gives you a lot of promises that you either think they are too good to be true or that you end up extremely disappointed.</span><br><span class="more">Read More...</span><span class="hide hide_more">Hide</span>
        </p>
        
        <h1 class="b_h1 mb1">What Ur Pets Life <span>Offers</span></h1>
        
        <div class="b_width close">
            
            <div class="offers_item">
