                    <h2>A Shopping Section</h2>
                    <p>With more than 80 brands that you can choose from for your Dog, Cat, Bird, Rabbit, Guinea Pig and more. With our 5 fixed and ongoing loyalty programs, you can end up saving more then 25%. To find out more please click on the “Loyalty Programs “ icon in the shopping section.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="offers_item">
                <img src="<%= asset_path 'about/offers/microchip.svg' %>">
                <div>
                    <h2>Centralized Microchip Database</h2>
                    <p>With a lot of people asking for a centralized microchip database so we can reunite the found pets with their owners, we have created that for all pet lovers instead of jumping from clinic to clinic to find out if this pet is registered with them.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="offers_item">
                <img src="<%= asset_path 'about/offers/messenger.svg' %>">
                <div>
                    <h2>Messenger System</h2>
                    <p>We have created our own messenger system that connects you with pets establishments and our shopping facility since using your private whatsupp is not favourable for everyone.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="offers_item">
                <img src="<%= asset_path 'about/offers/owner.svg' %>">
                <div>
                    <h2>Pet Business Owners</h2>
                    <p>If you are a pet business owner and would like to list your business and reach thousands of pet lovers free of charge, please contact us.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="offers_item">
                <img src="<%= asset_path 'about/offers/paw-multi-colored.svg' %>">
                <div>
                    <h2>Adoption Section</h2>
                    <p>An adoption section where every adoption agency out there can post their pets and reach out to thousands of Fur loving Humans to make finding a home for these lovely fur babies easier</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="offers_item">
                <img src="<%= asset_path 'about/offers/network.svg' %>">
                <div>
                    <h2>Connects Pet Owners</h2>
                    <p>Ur Pets Life connects pet owners to verified and trustworthy pet business around them such as boarding places, day care facilities, grooming salons, trainers and more</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="offers_item">
                <img src="<%= asset_path 'about/offers/passport-card.svg' %>">
                <div>
                    <h2>Digital Passport</h2>
                    <p>Are you tired of keeping your pets passport on hand at all time, or searching for it when you need to find some information about them? Well Ur Pets Life has created the first fully operational digital passport for your passport where you can track their weight history, health history, vaccinations reminders, and pictures so whenever you need to access these information it is as simple as a click of a button</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="offers_item">
                <img src="<%= asset_path 'about/offers/community.svg' %>">
                <div>
                    <h2>Community Page</h2>
                    <p>And of course we have created a community page on the mobile application where all users can chat, help each other and share pictures and videos with each other and that can only be seen by registered pet members. You no longer have to go through all the post to find what interest you, you can select your favourite topic and see the thread about it.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="offers_item">
                <img src="<%= asset_path 'about/offers/geofencing.svg' %>">
                <div>
                    <h2>Geo-Fencing technology</h2>
                    <p>All us dog and cat lovers, we follow a lot of pet social media groups and we end up seeing a lot of missing pets and heart broken parents. We couldn’t just stand and do nothing and only rely on posting about our missing pet and hope that someone in our community is online and checking our post so they can help us, so we ended up creating a Community Geo-Fencing technology where if God forbid we lost our pet, with just 1 click every pet lover in our community will be notified on the spot about our missing pet and his details so that they can help us search for it instantly since we all know the first 10 to 20 min are crucial to finding our pet.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
        </div>
		
		
